                    .vacancies-setup-2__data__tips__type__icon
                  .vacancies-setup-2__data__tips__chose
                    .vacancies-setup-2__data__tips__chose__icon
                    .vacancies-setup-2__data__tips__chose__label 已選擇題數：0/10
